\n|6\n|20 Jul 2012\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|THA}} {{small|Baan Khao Hom School, [[Chantaburi]], Thailand}}\n|\n|-\n|2\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|2\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|IDN}} Jemmy Gobel\n|{{abbr|PTS|Points decision}}\n|6\n|27 Jun 2012\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|THA}} {{small|[[Taweethapisek School]], [[Bangkok]], Thailand}}\n|\n|-\n|1\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|1\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|IDN}} Rino Ukru\n|{{abbr|TKO|Technical knockout}}\n|4 (6), {{small|0:30}}\n|18 May 2012\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|THA}} {{small|City Hall Ground, [[Nakhon Ratchasima]], Thailand}}\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{boxrec|id=613659}}\n*[http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1819129_1819134_1825954,00.html \"Amnat Ruenroeng\"], n\u00b056 on ''[[Time (magazine)|Time]]''\u2019s list of \"100 Olympic Athletes To Watch\"\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20080812085556/http://results.beijing2008.cn/WRM/ENG/BIO/Athlete/9/230249.shtml Results.beijing2008.cn - Bio]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20131005001918/http://88.85.4.2/biographies.fwx?id_athlete=3037 Biographies for Amnat Ruenroeng] [[International Boxing Association (amateur)|International Boxing Association]]\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-sports}}\n{{s-text|style=background:#C1D8FF; font-weight: bold;|text=Regional boxing titles}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-new}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[International Boxing Federation|IBF]] Asia [[flyweight]] champion\n|years=15 Feb 2013 \u2013 22 Jan 2014<br>Won world title}}\n{{s-vac}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=Ryan Rey Ponteras}}\n{{s-ttl|title=IBF Pan Pacific flyweight champion \n|years=19 Apr 2013 \u2013 Jul 2013}}\n{{s-vac}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-text|style=background:#C1D8FF; font-weight: bold;|text=World boxing titles}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=[[Moruti Mthalane]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of IBF world champions#Flyweight|IBF flyweight champion]]\n|years=22 Jan 2014 \u2013 25 May 2016}}\n{{s-aft|afte