ore|Victoria Street]], [[North Bridge Road]]-[[South Bridge Road]] and various roads in CBD\n\n===South Korea===\n[[File:Myeongdong2.JPG|thumb|[[Myeongdong]] in [[Seoul]]|220x220px]]\n*[[Busan]]: [[Gwangbok-dong]], [[Nampo-dong]], [[Seomyeon, Busan|Seomyeon]], [[Centum City]]\n*[[Daegu]]: [[Dongseongno]]\n*[[Daejeon]]: [[Eunhaeng-dong]], [[Dunsan]]\n*[[Gwangju]]: [[Chungjangno]], [[Geumnamno]], [[Sangmu]]\n*[[Seoul]]: [[Myeongdong]], [[Namdaemun Market]], [[Jongno]], [[Insa-dong]], [[Daehangno]], [[Dongdaemun Market]],<ref name=\"bbc.co.uk\"/> [[Apgujeong]], [[Cheongdam]], [[Itaewon]], [[Gangnam District|Gangnam]], [[Samseong-dong]], [[Yongsan]], [[Sinchon-dong, Seoul|Sinchon]], [[Hongdae area|Hongdae]], [[Yeongdeungpo]]\n\n===Taiwan===\n[[File:Pacific Sogo Taipei Zhongxiao Store 20091124 night.jpg|right|thumb|Taipei Da'an|220x220px]]\n\n*[[Taipei]]: [[Da'an District, Taipei|Da'an]], [[Xinyi District|Xinyi]], [[Tianmu, Shilin District|Tianmu]]\n*[[Kaohsiung]]: [[Cianjhen District|Cianjhen]]\n\n===Thailand===\n*[[Bangkok]]: [[Ratchaprasong]], [[Sukhumvit Road]], [[Thong Lor]], [[Siam Square]], [[Si Lom]], [[Victory Monument, Bangkok|Victory Monument]], [[Lat Phrao District|Ladprao]], [[Ratchada]], [[Chatuchak (district)|Chatuchak]], [[Wang Lang]], [[Bang Lumphu]] - [[Khao San Road]], [[Phahurat]] - [[Sampeng]], [[Bobae]]\n*[[Chiang Mai]]: [[Changkran Road]], [[Nimmanhemin Rd]]\n*[[Hat Yai]]: [[Kimyong Market]], [[Niphat Uthit 1st, 2nd, 3rd Roads]], [[Sanehanusorn Road]]\n*[[Pattaya]]: [[Beach Road (Pattaya)|Beach Road]]\n*[[Patong]]: [[Patong Beach Road]]\n*[[Si Racha]]: [[Si Racha Nakorn Road]]\n\n===Vietnam===\n*[[Ho Chi Minh City]] ([[Saigon]]): [[District 1, Ho Chi Minh City|District 1]], [[Nguyen Trai Street]]\n*[[Ho Chi Minh City]] ([[Saigon]]): [[District 1, Ho Chi Minh City|District 1]], [[Dong Khoi Street]]\n*[[Ho Chi Minh City]] ([[Saigon]]): [[District 1, Ho Chi Minh City|District 1]], [[De Tham Street]]\n*[[Ho Chi Minh City]] ([[Saigon]]): [[District 1, H