an Street]], [[Canglang]], [[Pingjiang Road]]\n<!--\n====Jilin====\n-->\n\n====Liaoning====\n[[File:\u9752\u6ce5\u6d3c\u6865.JPG|thumb|[[Qingniwaqiao]] in [[Dalian]], [[Liaoning Province]], [[China]]]]\n*[[Dalian]]: [[Qingniwaqiao]], [[Xi'an Road Commercial Zone|Xi'an Road]], Heping Square\n<!--\n====Ningxia====\n====Qinghai====\n-->\n\n====Shaanxi====\n*[[Xi'an]]: [[Eastern Street, Xian|Eastern Street]]\n\n====Shandong====\n*[[Qingdao]]: Taidong\n\n====Shanghai====\n[[File:Shanghai - Nanjing Road.jpeg|thumb|right|[[Nanjing Road (Shanghai)|Nanjing Road]], [[Shanghai]]]]\n*[[Nanjing Road East]], [[Nanjing Road West]]\n*[[Avenue Joffre]]\n*[[People's Square]]\n*[[Zikawei]]\n*[[Lujiazui]]\n*[[The Bund (Shanghai)|The Bund]]\n*[[Wujiaochang]]\n*[[Avenue Petain]]\n*[[Jing'an Temple]]\n*[[Dapu Bridge]]\n*[[Zhongshan Park]]\n*[[Hongqiao Subdistrict, Shanghai|Hongqiao]]\n*[[City God Temple]]\n*[[Xintiandi]]\n*[[Daning, Shanghai|Daning]]\n*[[Huamu]]\n*[[Tianzifang]]\n*[[Zhujiajiao]]\n*[[French Concession]]\n*[[Shanghai Railway Station]]\n*[[Qibao]]\n*[[Xinzhuang, Shanghai|Xinzhuang]]\n*[[Shanghai Stadium]]\n*[[North Sichuan Road]]\n*[[Sinan Road]]\n\n<!--\n====Shanxi====\n-->\n\n====Sichuan====\n*[[Chengdu]]: Chunxilu: including dozens of shopping malls and over 700 shops and thousands of restaurants;\nHongxinglu: (close to Chunxilu) dozens of shopping malls of luxury goods;\nWorld Center : biggest building in the world with several hotels, one cinema, hundreds of restaurants, one skating rink, one aqua park and an artificial beach, two shopping malls, one supermarket etc. inside this building\n<!--\n====Tibet====\n====Xinjiang====\n====Yunnan====\n-->\n\n====Zhejiang====\n*[[Hangzhou]]: [[Wulin Square]], [[Euro Street, Hubin Road]], [https://web.archive.org/web/20121025124838/http://www.hzmixc.com/ The MixC]\n*[[Ningbo]]: [[Tianyi Square]]\n\n===Hong Kong===\n[[File:HK Parklane Avenue.jpg|right|thumb|[[Nathan Road, Hong Kong]]]]\n*[[Hong Kong Island]]: [[Causeway Bay]],<ref>