aramachi]], [[Shij\u014d Karasuma]]), [[Pontoch\u014d]], [[Shin-Ky\u014dgoku Street]]\n*[[Nagoya]]: [[:Ja:\u540d\u99c5|Meieki]] (district around [[Nagoya Station]]), [[Sakae Station (Aichi)|Sakae]], [[:Ja:\u91d1\u5c71 (\u540d\u53e4\u5c4b\u5e02)|Kanayama]]\n*[[Osaka]]: [[Umeda]], [[Mid\u014dsuji]], Minami area ([[Amerikamura|America-mura]], [[D\u014dtonbori]], [[Horie]], [[Namba]], [[Nipponbashi]], [[Shinsaibashi]], and [[Sennichimae]]), [[Tenn\u014dji-ku, Osaka|Tenn\u014dji]]\n*[[Sapporo]]: [[Odori Park]], [[:Ja:\u72f8\u5c0f\u8def\u5546\u5e97\u8857|Tanuki K\u014dji]]\n*[[Sendai]]: [[Ichibanch\u014d]], [[Chu\u014d Street]]\n*[[Tokyo]]: [[Aoyama, Tokyo|Aoyama]], [[Asakusa]], [[Daikanyama]], [[Ebisu, Tokyo|Ebisu]], [[Ginza]],<ref name=\"bbc.co.uk\"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cnbc.com/id/21917314/?photo=5 |title=The World's Most Expensive Shopping Districts |publisher=CNBC |date=2007-11-21 |accessdate=2012-08-15 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015172510/http://www.cnbc.com/id/21917314/?photo=5 |archivedate=15 October 2012 |df=dmy-all }}</ref> [[Harajuku]], [[Ikebukuro]], [[Jiyugaoka]], [[Nihonbashi]], <!-- not shopping street [[Odaiba]], -->[[Omotesand\u014d, Tokyo|Omotesand\u014d]], [[Roppongi]], [[Shibuya, Tokyo|Shibuya]], [[Shimokitazawa]], [[Shinjuku]], [[Y\u016brakuch\u014d]]\n*[[Western Tokyo]]: [[Kichij\u014dji]], [[Machida, Tokyo|Machida]], [[Tachikawa]], [[Hachi\u014dji]]\n*[[Yokohama]]: [[Minato Mirai 21]], [[Motomachi, Yokohama|Motomachi]], [[Yokohama Chinatown]]\n*[[Kawasaki, Kanagawa|Kawasaki]]: [[Kawasaki-ku, Kawasaki|Kawasaki]]\n*[[Saitama Prefecture|Saitama]]: [[\u014cmiya, Saitama|\u014cmiya]], [[Urawa-ku, Saitama|Urawa]]\n*[[Chiba Prefecture|Chiba]]: [[Chiba, Chiba|Chiba]], [[Kashiwa, Chiba|Kashiwa]], [[Funabashi, Chiba|Funabashi]]\n\n===Kuwait===\n*[[Kuwait City]]: [[Salmiya]] - [[Salem Al-Mubarak Street]]\n\n===Lebanon===\n[[File:An der K\u00fcste Beirut center.jpg|thumb|Maarad street, [[Beirut]]]]\n*[[Beirut]]: [