igsstra\u00dfe]]\n* [[Kiel]]: [[Holstenstra\u00dfe]], [[D\u00e4nische Stra\u00dfe]]\n* [[Leipzig]]: [[Petersstra\u00dfe]], [[Grimmaische Stra\u00dfe]]\n* [[Mannheim]]: [[Planken (Mannheim)|Planken]]\n* [[Munich]]: [[Kaufingerstra\u00dfe]],<ref name=\"bbc.co.uk\"/> [[Neuhauser Stra\u00dfe]], upscale: [[Theatinerstra\u00dfe]], [[Maximilianstra\u00dfe (Munich)|Maximilianstra\u00dfe]]\n* [[M\u00f6nchengladbach]]: [[Hindenburgstra\u00dfe (M\u00f6nchengladbach)|Hindenburgstra\u00dfe]]\n* [[Nuremberg]]: [[Karolinenstra\u00dfe]]\n* [[Stuttgart]]: [[K\u00f6nigstra\u00dfe (Stuttgart)|K\u00f6nigstra\u00dfe]]\n* [[Wiesbaden]]: [[Wilhelmstra\u00dfe (Wiesbaden)|Wilhelmstra\u00dfe]], [[Kirchgasse]]\n\n===Greece===\n*[[Athens]]: [[Voukourestiou Street]], [[Ermou Street]], [[Kassaveti Street]]\n*[[Thessaloniki]]: [[Tsimiski Street]] [[Medditeranean Cosmos]]\n\n===Hungary===\n*[[Budapest]]: [[Andr\u00e1ssy Avenue]], [[V\u00e1ci utca]], De\u00e1k utca\n*[[Szeged]]: [[K\u00e1r\u00e1sz Street]],\n\n===Ireland===\n*[[Dublin]]: [[Grafton Street]],<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cnbc.com/id/21917314/?photo=4 |title=The World's Most Expensive Shopping Districts |publisher=CNBC |date=2007-11-21 |accessdate=2012-08-15 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015172538/http://www.cnbc.com/id/21917314/?photo=4 |archivedate=15 October 2012 |df=dmy-all }}</ref> [[Henry Street (Dublin)|Henry Street]], [[O'Connell Street]], [[Wicklow Street]], [[North Earl Street]]\n*[[Cork (city)|Cork]]: [[St. Patrick's Street]], Oliver Plunkett Street\n*[[Galway]]: [[Shop Street]]\n*[[Limerick]]: [[O'Connell Street, Limerick|O'Connell Street]]\n*[[Swords, Dublin|Swords]]: Main Street\n*[[Drogheda]]: West Street\n\n===Iceland===\n*[[Reykjav\u00edk]]: [[Laugavegur (Reykjav\u00edk)|Laugavegur]]\n\n===Italy===\n[[File:Palazzo Strozzi 01.JPG|thumb|[[Via de' Tornabuoni]] in [[Florence]]]]\n[[File:fontana.della.barcaccia.arp.jpg|thumb|right|[[Via Condotti]] in [[Rome]]]]\n*[[Bari]]: [[Via Sparano]]